  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the chicken to the skillet and cook until browned and cooked through.",
    "Remove the chicken from the skillet and set aside.",
    "Add the garlic to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes to the skillet and cook for 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the cooked chicken back to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "To serve, place a scoop of khao khuah rice in the bottom of a dolsot stone bowl.",
    "Add the chicken and tomato mixture on top of the rice.",
    "Serve immediately."
